PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775909466
OL,3,CGovernment invests #380m into Somerset
OL,4,CTata battery factory
OL,6,FThe government has invested nearly
OL,7,F#400 million into Somerset's new
OL,8,Felectric vehicle battery gigafactory.
OL,10,FThe Agratas factory, near Bridgwater,
OL,11,Fwill supply batteries to electric
OL,12,Fvehicles produced by Jaguar Land Rover
OL,13,Fand is expected to open by the end of
OL,14,F2027.
OL,16,FIt will create more than 4,000 jobs in
OL,17,Fthe area, which the Business secretary
OL,18,FPeter Kyle MP said will ensure the
OL,19,Ffactory thrives for decades to come.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775909466
OL,3,CGovernment invests #380m into Somerset
OL,4,CTata battery factory
OL,6,F"When it comes to batteries for cars,
OL,7,FChina has stolen a march - it's very
OL,8,Fhard to compete with them on
OL,9,Finnovation and pricing," he said.
OL,11,F"But by this government being an
OL,12,Factive partner, alongside Agratas,
OL,13,FJaguar Land Rover and the people of
OL,14,FSomerset, we can make this site
OL,15,Fcommercially viable, but also cutting-
OL,16,Fedge in terms of the research and
OL,17,Fdevelopment."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775909466
OL,3,CGovernment invests #380m into Somerset
OL,4,CTata battery factory
OL,6,FHe added the government has been
OL,7,Fassured by Agratas that the new
OL,8,Ffactory will keep pace with
OL,9,Fdevelopments in battery technology.
OL,11,F"These are things that we've
OL,12,Fconsidered as a government supporting
OL,13,FTata (Agratas' parent company) in its
OL,14,Finvestment here, and the people who
OL,15,Fare committing their time to come and
OL,16,Fwork, and their professional
OL,17,Fexpertise, can rest assured that they
OL,18,Fwill be doing so for decades to come,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
OL,26,@zD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
