OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775909466
OL,3,CGovernment invests #380m into Somerset
OL,4,CTata battery factory
OL,6,FEarl Wiggins, Agratas' vice-president
OL,7,Fof UK manufacturing operations, added:
OL,8,F"We welcome the government's
OL,9,Finvestment as we build a battery
OL,10,Fmanufacturing facility that will play
OL,11,Fa vital role in delivering net zero
OL,12,Fand strengthening the UK's position as
OL,13,Fa global leader in battery
OL,14,Fmanufacturing.
OL,16,F"This funding will support the
OL,17,Fdevelopment of our Somerset facility,
OL,18,Fenabling us to produce battery cells
OL,19,Ffor our anchor customer, Jaguar Land
OL,20,FRover.
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775909466
OL,3,CGovernment invests #380m into Somerset
OL,4,CTata battery factory
OL,6,F"Over the next year, we will have over
OL,7,F2,200 people working on the site, and
OL,8,Fthat growth will continue over the
OL,9,Fcoming years."
OL,11,FThe funding comes as part of the
OL,12,Fgovernment's industrial strategy which
OL,13,Fis providing #700 million of
OL,14,Finvestment into Britain's advanced
OL,15,Fmanufacturing sector ` with the
OL,16,Fgigafactory being the largest single
OL,17,Fbeneficiary.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]
